#!/bin/bash
# HW4-A checker (Q1: K- interpreter, Q2: tree.k-).
# Build: dune (the provided parser is Menhir). Tests: per-file in examples/ and exercises/.
cd "$(dirname "$0")" || exit 1

RUN=./_build/default/bin/main.exe
TIMEOUT=10
WRONG="$(tput setaf 1)✗$(tput sgr0)"
CORRECT="$(tput setaf 2)✓$(tput sgr0)"

# compare: $1 = .ans file, $2 = actual output file.
# An .ans starting with "Runtime Error :" matches by prefix (error-type), else exact.
compare () {
    local ans out
    ans="$(cat "$1")"
    out="$(cat "$2")"
    if [[ "$ans" == "Runtime Error :"* ]]; then
        [[ "$out" == "$ans"* ]]
    else
        [[ "$out" == "$ans" ]]
    fi
}

run_one () {  # $1 = .k- file to run, $2 = .ans, $3 = .out, $4 = optional .in
    if [[ -n "$4" && -f "$4" ]]; then
        timeout "$TIMEOUT" "$RUN" "$1" < "$4" > "$3" 2>/dev/null
    else
        timeout "$TIMEOUT" "$RUN" "$1" > "$3" 2>/dev/null
    fi
    compare "$2" "$3"
}

# Q1: run examples/test*.k- directly.
check_q1 () {
    echo "# Exercise 1 (K- interpreter)"
    local pass=0 total=0
    for kf in examples/test*.k-; do
        [ -e "$kf" ] || continue
        total=$((total + 1))
        local base="${kf%.k-}"
        printf "Test %s..." "$(basename "$base")"
        if run_one "$kf" "${base}.ans" "${base}.out" "${base}.in"; then
            pass=$((pass + 1)); echo "$CORRECT"
        else
            echo "$WRONG"
            diff "${base}.ans" "${base}.out" | sed 's/^/    /'
        fi
    done
    echo "Passed ${pass}/${total} Cases"
}

# Q2: inject each exercises/test*.k- snippet into tree.k- at the 2026 marker.
check_q2 () {
    echo "# Exercise 2 (tree.k-)"
    local pass=0 total=0
    for kf in exercises/test*.k-; do
        [ -e "$kf" ] || continue
        total=$((total + 1))
        local base="${kf%.k-}"
        local tmp="${base}.tmp.k-"
        sed -e "/2026/ r ${kf}" -e "s/2026//" tree.k- > "$tmp"
        printf "Test %s..." "$(basename "$base")"
        if run_one "$tmp" "${base}.ans" "${base}.out"; then
            pass=$((pass + 1)); echo "$CORRECT"
        else
            echo "$WRONG"
            diff "${base}.ans" "${base}.out" | sed 's/^/    /'
        fi
        rm -f "$tmp"
    done
    echo "Passed ${pass}/${total} Cases"
}

echo '# Compiling...'
if ! dune build --profile release 2>&1; then
    echo ''
    echo 'Compile fail.'
    exit 1
fi
echo ''

if [[ $# -eq 0 ]]; then
    echo "== Homework 4-A =="
    check_q1
    check_q2
elif [[ "$1" == "1" ]]; then
    check_q1
elif [[ "$1" == "2" ]]; then
    check_q2
else
    echo "Error: Exercise $1 not found"
fi
